<p>
  When going through my decal stash, I came across the set of
  {{ 'TigerHead decals' | linkTo('http://www.tigerheaddecals.com/') | safe }} (48008)
  that I had used for {{ 'one of my Tamiya Spitfires' | linkTo('../../2016/0301/') | safe }}
